    <h4 id="list-item-1">Introduction</h4>
      <p>Chiara Ferrero-Wong is currently studying at McGill University in the Masters of Information Studies program. 
        Before beginning this degree, she worked in the clean and renewable energy sector in communications, outreach, and GIS. 
            Her undergraduate degree was in environmental science and English from Dalhousie University.
            Chiara is passionate about environmental sustainability and equity, and is driven by her desire to build a resilient
            community in the face of climate change. 
            In addition to her academic and professional pursuits, Chiara enjoys reading, spending time outside, and playing
            ultimate frisbee. Chiara also enjoys making vlogs of the trips she goes on with her friends and family.
      </p>
 
